{"tid":1868682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個時候啲環保撚見到咁多即棄口罩會有咩感受？","createTime":"2020-02-07T17:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T15:23:25.000Z","uid":2104,"like":31,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9b8ca8b9a00f90ae4dce8013025d3a47698973","tid":1868682,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"啲口罩用完即棄好唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前我因為衛生問題想拎支飲管都唔比<br />\n而家唔單止飲管要獨立包裝<br />\n就連啲即棄消毒酒精紙都用多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環保撚呢一刻有咩感受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲好記得之前有次落雨行商場<br />\n個管理員已經叫人用遮袋入好啲遮唔好比啲雨水整濕地下避免跣親人<br />\n但係有條環保撚仲話人哋唔環保點點點<br />\n大佬呀 你把遮啲雨水倒流番落地下到時跣親人除時命都冇<br />\n喺環保 安全 同衛生都唔識點平衡就學人講環保<br />\n其實最偽善同自私中意強加自己諗法落人哋度就係呢啲環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902e3dad61425f56bf7d46ee5994838e95897172","tid":1868682,"uid":37389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"搶埋一份"},{"pid":"a0fa4c8804af9aa31078dee87d6cc5d0ec5b7b98","tid":1868682,"uid":163954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:08:32.000Z","msg":"二手口罩"},{"pid":"c51f308ff0a76a53d35c946eefee5fc70660ea6b","tid":1868682,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"其實環保撚最後目的係環保屌+環保吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcf9932d09f14b72a358c1543ec83e7a4d342a7","tid":1868682,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"ea9b8ca8b9a00f90ae4dce8013025d3a47698973","tid":1868682,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"啲口罩用完即棄好唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前我因為衛生問題想拎支飲管都唔比<br />\n而家唔單止飲管要獨立包裝<br />\n就連啲即棄消毒酒精紙都用多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環保撚呢一刻有咩感受？